en teacher complain about a child student is being lazy or poor learner, the parents should  consult   a capable doctor for exact reasoning why a child is performing poorly in the school.[/quote]', 0, 1, '24.156.114.9', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'on_nl2br', 4764, 143639),
