(126642, 903, 24207, 'Vik', 1507, '', 1279059225, 'Ok. Trying to reply for various posts over here. \nRegarding stoning of stray dogs, not a humane way to get rid of them. But get rid we must.\nSince we all here know that dogs require proper vacinnation. And therefore, straydogs possess grave threat to us, b/c they are not vacinnated. \n\nDogs must be kept for livestock ptotection and hunting. Some jurists have stated that they \ncan be kept as guard dogs(house). But not all jurists agree. \n\nRegarding pedigree dogs, I have seen many of them at empress market. All dognapping cases.\nAnd pedigree dogs, more expensive than a gun so we might wanna make a choice.', 0, 1, '115.186.70.9', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'on_nl2br', 1271, 144363),
