(132147, 3861, 131713, 'Usama', 241, '', 1280943360, 'In my view Polygonal rifling lasts longer than standard barrels with jacket bullets.\n\n[u]Advantages Of  Polygonal Rifling[/u]\n \nThe projectile is provided with better grip because of gas seal as polygonal bores tend to have \na slightly smaller bore area\n\nThe bullet gets less deforms causing greater muzzle velocity (since it pases easily)\n\nBetter accuracy and greater muzzle velocities because of greater consistency\n\nLess buildup of Carbon or Lead in the gun hence Easier to Clean ... Resulting to Longer Barrel LIfe..', 0, 1, '119.155.40.102', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'on_nl2br', 5452, 150426),
